<Layout>
    
	<body>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
        <a href="/about/">About</a>
        <h1>My Astro Site</h1>
         <h1>About Me</h1>
        <h2>... and my new Astro site!</h2>

        <p>I am working through <pre>Astro's introductory tutorial</pre>. This is the second page on my website, and it's the first one I built myself!</p>

